 america it owns equipment and the leases on real property of united states antimony mexico sa de cv usamsa it has interests in antimony de mexico sa de cv am which owns the san miguel concession of the los juarez property usamsa has various divisions which include the madero smelter in coahuila the puerto blanco flotation mill and oxide circuit in guanajuato and mining properties that include the los juarez mineral deposit with concessions in queretaro the wadley mining concession in san lis potosi the soyatal deposits in queretaro and the guadalupe properties in zacatecasthe companys montana smelter processes feed from canadian mexican and australian sources recovers metals and makes finished antimony oxide and metal the companys madero smelter produces antimony from mexico the company produces antimony metal oxide sodium antimonite and metals from its processing facility near thompson falls montana the company also sells antimony metal for use in bearings storage batteries and ordnancezeolite divisionthe company owns bear river zeolite company brz which has a lease with webster farm llc which allows brz to surface mine and process zeolite on property located near preston idaho in addition brz has zeolite on the united states bureau of land management land the property has approximately two dryer circuits one for lines one and two and one for the raymond mill the dryer circuits include an approximately  ton feed bin and each dryer has a conveyor bypass around each dryer a bucket elevator and a dry rock bin its raymond mill circuit includes a  highside raymond mill with a double whizzer dust collector approximately two  ton product silos feed bin conveyors air slide bucket elevators and control booth the raymond mill has a rated capacity of over  tons per hour » full overview of uamya company address united states antimony corp p o box thompson falls   mt    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation john lawrence  daniel parks  russell 